Sentencas: The performance of multi-layer (1 - x)La0.8Sr0.2MnO3/xYSZ graded composite cathodes was studied as electrode materials for intermediate solid oxide fuel cells (SOFC).
Titulo: Fabrication and performance of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3/YSZ graded composite cathodes for SOFC

Sentencas: The thermal expansion coefficient, electrical conductivity, and electrochemical performance of multi-layer composite cathodes were investigated.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3/YSZ graded composite cathodes for SOFC

Sentencas: The thermal expansion coefficient and electrical conductivity decreased with the increase in YSZ content.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3/YSZ graded composite cathodes for SOFC

Sentencas: The (1 - x)La0.8Sr0.2MnO3/xYSZ composite cathode greatly increased the length of the active triple phase boundary line (TPBL) among electrode, electrolyte, and gas phase, leading to a decrease in polarization resistance and an increase in polarization current density.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3/YSZ graded composite cathodes for SOFC

Sentencas: The polarization current density of the triple-layer graded composite cathode (0.77 A/cm(2)) was the highest and that of the monolayer cathode (0.13 A/cm(2)) was the lowest.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3/YSZ graded composite cathodes for SOFC

Sentencas: The polarization resistance (R-P) of the triple-layer graded composite cathode was only 0.182 Omega.cm(2) and that of the monolayer composite cathode was 0.323 Omega.cm(2).
Titulo: Fabrication and performance of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3/YSZ graded composite cathodes for SOFC

Sentencas: The power density of the triple-layer graded composite cathode was the highest and that of the monolayer composite cathode was the lowest.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3/YSZ graded composite cathodes for SOFC

Sentencas: The triple-layer graded composite cathode had superior performance.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3/YSZ graded composite cathodes for SOFC
